# AdoptCheck environment variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values you need.
# .env.local is gitignored and is loaded automatically by `next dev` / `next build`.
# AdoptCheck runs fully in deterministic mode with NONE of these set — they are all optional.

# --- Optional: GitHub API ---
# Increases the GitHub API rate limit from 60 to 5000 requests/hour.
# Create a fine-grained or classic token with public read scope only.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxx

# --- Optional: LLM analyst layer (via OpenRouter) ---
# When set, AdoptCheck adds an evidence-grounded analyst interpretation on top of the
# deterministic report. Without it, the analyst layer is simply skipped.
# Get a key at https://openrouter.ai/keys (format: sk-or-v1-...).
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-xxx

# Optional analyst model override. Must be a valid OpenRouter model id that supports
# structured (json_schema) output. Defaults to "openai/gpt-4o-mini".
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=openai/gpt-4o-mini

# Optional metadata sent to OpenRouter for attribution (shown on your OpenRouter dashboard).
# OPENROUTER_SITE_URL=https://adoptcheck.nullhype.tech
# OPENROUTER_APP_NAME=AdoptCheck

# --- Optional: usage metering + payments ---
# When these are set, AdoptCheck meters anonymous devices: 3 free repo checks
# (ac_sid cookie), then paid one-time credits via Dodo Payments. If they are
# NOT set, metering fails open and every scan is free.

# Supabase project used for the adoptcheck_sessions metering table (server-only,
# service role). Can reuse the same project as HypeCheck. See
# supabase/adoptcheck_sessions.sql for the one-time table setup.
# SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOi...

# Override the free-scan limit (default 3).
# ADOPTCHECK_FREE_LIMIT=3

# Dodo Payments (same account as HypeCheck; reuse DODO_SECRET_KEY / DODO_WEBHOOK_SECRET).
# DODO_SECRET_KEY=...
# DODO_WEBHOOK_SECRET=...
# DODO_ENVIRONMENT=live_mode            # or test_mode
# DODO_PRODUCT_ID_SINGLE=prod_xxx       # $2.99 -> 1 credit
# DODO_PRODUCT_ID_PACK=prod_xxx         # $4.99 -> 20 credits

# Base URL used for the post-checkout return link.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://adoptcheck.nullhype.tech
